  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf   \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Wife Arrested for Killing Husband with Spade",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A woman and her son who killed a 51-year-old man from Badulai-Kahataruppa area with a spade have been arrested by the police.",
        "The deceased's 33-year-old wife and his 17-year-old son have also been arrested.",
        "In this situation, on June 16, a body was recovered from the forest 200 meters away from the suspect's house, which had been bitten and mutilated by animals.",
        "After the report of the Badula court regarding this body, the Badula magistrate Sujith da Silva had issued an order to arrest the suspects related to this incident.",
        "In this regard, the suspect's wife told the police that the father objected to her son's love and tortured her son and thus killed her husband with a spade while he was sleeping.",
        "It is reported that she committed the murder on the night of 31st May and threw the dead body in the forest along with her son the next night and reported her husband missing at the police station that day.",
        "The mother and son have been remanded and the Badulai police are carrying out investigations related to the incident."
      ],
